<author>Suakliana</author>
<title>Puitu Thagau Thiengtho</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalmang Na Thagau chun ei pui zingin,
 Lei mun gimtheihna laka hin;
 Hukdamna kulhpi sunga leng dingin,
 Nang hun gingte pui hatin.

[V2]
 Van gam zuonin ei puiin,
 Zinmang dona cheng zo di'n;
 Thepna dogal chu zo ngei ungkau,
 Chun Na vak ah leng ungkau.

[V3]
 2. Van Lal Thagau I kipuih sak laiin,
 Zinmang tawngsie a mang zel hi;
 Khawvel buoi leh dahumna nuoisieh in,
 Van gam laituol ah leng kau.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa Thagau puih loh chun khawvel hi,
 Sang tamtak manna gam ahi;
 Gam nuom mang loin ei tun tei intin,
 Lalpa, Na hatna muongin.

[V5]
 4. Dahum cheng nuom takin thuok zel hitiu,
 Hatlo Lalpa'n panpih ei tiem;
 Thagau in lam tawnin ei pui intin,
 Mun lopi I tun chan un.</lyrics>
</song>